Detailed Description

cvmx_sli_pkt::_vf_int_sum

This register contains summary interrupts bits for a VF. A VF read of this register for any of its 8 rings will return the same 8-bit summary for packet input, packet output and mailbox interrupts. If a PF reads this register it will return 0x0.
